# ── AI Providers (set at least ONE — free options available) ──────────────────
#
# OPTION A — OpenAI (paid, best quality)
#   Get key: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY="sk-..."

# OPTION B — Google Gemini Flash (FREE — no credit card needed)
#   Free tier: 1,500 requests/day, 1,000,000 tokens/minute
#   Get key: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY="AIza..."

# OPTION C — Groq / Llama 3.3 70B (FREE — no credit card needed)
#   Free tier: 14,400 requests/day, 500,000 tokens/day, ultra-fast
#   Get key: https://console.groq.com/keys
GROQ_API_KEY="gsk_..."

# You can set all three — the system tries them in order:
#   OpenAI → Gemini → Groq (automatic fallback on failure/rate limit)
#
# Minimum free setup (totally free, no CC):
#   Set GEMINI_API_KEY + GROQ_API_KEY
#   Groq acts as backup when Gemini hits daily limit

